oracle.xml.comp

Class CXMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.xml.comp.CXMLParser

  •  
    public class CXMLParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the re-generation of XML document from the compressed stream by generating the SAX events from them.
